  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-size: large">
    <b>Using the small Tag for Disclaimers</b>
    <p>
      Winning projects will be announced on our website.
      <small>All decisions are final.</small>
    </p>
    <b>Using the small Tag for Copyright Information</b>
    <p><small>&copy; 2023 Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</small></p>
  </body>
</html>
